Berthe Jalabert https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Berthe_Jalabert 0 Berthe Jalabert (Rennes, 31 October 1858 – after 1935) was a French stage and film actress. She was the daughter of the actor, theatre director and playwright Louis Péricaud (1835-1909). Berthe_Jalabert ( Rennes , 31_October_1858 – after 1935 ) was a_French_stage_and_film_actress .
